data.description: Come experience 4061 Kennedy Ct, a fantastic opportunity in a convenient location near the highway. This cozy brick ranch home offers a variety of features that make it an excellent find. Enjoy the comfort of three spacious bedrooms, all located on the main level. This home boasts two full bathrooms on the main level. One-car garage. The front yard is fenced, providing a secure space for pets to play or for you to relax and enjoy the outdoors. The unfinished basement is not included in the square footage, but it offers endless possibilities. You could create extra rooms like a den, hobby room, or a bonus room to suit your needs. There's also a full bathroom in the basement, making it a versatile space for various activities. There's a workshop area for those who love DIY projects. Located on a dead end road. The property is being sold "as is," giving you the opportunity to put your personal touch on this home. Don't miss your chance to make this house your own.
